[[File:Map of state atheism.svg|thumb|right|500px|{{longitem |font-size:105%;padding-bottom:0.3em;border-bottom:1px solid #aaa}}|World map showing nations that formerly and currently practice state atheism. Most countries that practice and have practiced state atheism were [[Communist state|Communist countries]], with notable exceptions included [[Dechristianization of France during the French Revolution|France during the French First Republic]] and Mexico during the [[Cristero War]]. In addition, some Communist states like [[Somalia]] did not adopt state atheism and instead blended [[Marxism-Leninism|Marxist-Leninist]] social policies with the existing state religion of the country at the time.

